n earlier statement the FBI said that along with the US justice department it was investigating possible civil rights violations in connection with the threats . The Anti-Defamation League , a Jewish anti-bigotry organisation , said in a statement that it was &quot; deeply disturbed &quot; by the latest threats to the Jewish community . Meanwhile , more than 100 headstones have been damaged at a Jewish cemetery in St Louis , Missouri , local media report . In the Canadian city of Toronto , Mayor John Tory has condemned anti-Semitic hate notes left outside the homes of Jewish residents .
